query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('ado.net',
'angularjs-ng-repeat',
'comparison',
'cpanel',
'gtk',
'java-native-interface',
'jbutton',
'localization',
'postman',
'sonarqube',
'web-config')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Benefactor',
'Cleanup',
'Electorate',
'Fanatic',
'Favorite Question',
'Mortarboard',
'Populist',
'Proofreader',
'Pundit',
'Reviewer',
'Suffrage',
'Unsung Hero')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('codereview',
'magento',
'stackoverflow')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
